## Overview
- **Project:** BitBasis - Bitcoin Portfolio & Cost Basis Tracker
- **Stack:** 
  - **Frontend:** Next.js 14 (App Router), TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, shadcn/ui components
  - **Backend:** Supabase (Auth, Database, Storage, RLS policies), Node.js
  - **APIs:** Coinpaprika (Bitcoin price data), CoinMarketCap (Fear & Greed Index)
  - **Data Visualization:** Chart.js, Recharts, ApexCharts
  - **Form Management:** React Hook Form, Zod validation
  - **CSV Processing:** PapaParse
  - **Utilities:** date-fns, sonner (toast notifications)

## Summary
- **BitBasis** is a comprehensive Bitcoin portfolio tracker focused on cost basis calculations and transaction history management
- **Privacy-First Approach:** No exchange API integrations required, all data is user-uploaded and protected with Row Level Security
- **Comprehensive Analytics:** Calculates cost basis using multiple methods (FIFO, LIFO, Average), tracks unrealized gains, and provides detailed performance metrics
- **CSV Import System:** Supports various exchange formats with preview and validation functionality
- **Responsive Dashboard:** Mobile-friendly interface with dark mode support
- **Multi-view Analysis:** Dashboard overview, detailed performance tracking, portfolio composition breakdown, and complete transaction history 